extendedInterpretations.comment: In what Zand calls 'section 1.6' of CUT 22. It appears alongside DIN ('grapes') in a fragment regarding abundant gifts of Enlil, and a later a similar phrase appears in 3.1, with dates, figs, grapes and pomegranates (?).
In CUT 6:58-59, Enki eats the food of URUDAxSZAR2 and drinks the water from the well.
